Due to my life plan, I chose this school to study in order to get a better pass. I completed my degree in 2020 and received my diploma in the same year. Finally, after waiting for several years, I was able to apply for a better pass, and I took my proud academic qualifications for certification. I spent a lot of money and time waiting for the results, but a few months later the certification company informed me that the academic qualifications I submitted were fake.

I don't know what went wrong within the school, but I also ask the person in charge of the school to be responsible, even if it is not your fault. You already know that the academic qualifications of some students are fake. Please be responsible in informing the victimized students by email or phone.
